"1 pound dried Great Northern beans (2 1/2 cups)","1 cup diced dry-cured Spanish chorizo","4 cups chopped onion","8  garlic cloves, thinly sliced","4 cups water","2 tablespoons chopped fresh oregano","2 tablespoons chopped fresh thyme","1 1/2 teaspoons salt","1 teaspoon ground cumin","1/2 teaspoon smoked paprika","1/2 teaspoon paprika","2  bay leaves","2 tablespoons brown sugar","3 tablespoons no-salt-added tomato paste","3 tablespoons molasses","1/4 teaspoon crushed red pepper","2 1/2 tablespoons red wine vinegar","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","1/8 teaspoon ground red pepper","1/2 cup chopped green onions","2 tablespoons chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley"